answers.body_markdown:
The main problem that you have is in mixing `javax.` dependency with `jakarta.` dependency in the project to fix it remove all `javax.` dependency to `jakarta.` because you are using spring boot &gt; 3.x

    &lt;parent&gt;
            &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
            &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;
            &lt;version&gt;3.1.3&lt;/version&gt;
            &lt;relativePath/&gt; &lt;!-- lookup parent from repository --&gt;
        &lt;/parent&gt;

that was moved to `jakarta` from [3.x version][1].

Instead of:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;javax.activation&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;javax.activation-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;1.2.0&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

Add it:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;jakarta.activation&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;jakarta.activation-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.1.2&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

Also a little bit about your `pom.xml` file:

Remove:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;javax.validation&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;validation-api&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;2.0.1.Final&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

And instead of it add next one:

    &lt;dependency&gt;
        &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;
        &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-validation&lt;/artifactId&gt;
        &lt;version&gt;3.1.3&lt;/version&gt;
    &lt;/dependency&gt;

Also in your code you will have to replace all `javax.` imports to `jakarta.`.


  [1]: https://spring.io/blog/2022/05/24/preparing-for-spring-boot-3-0

